| **nanovms** | kooshapari | 31 | 0 | 0 | Clean, on main |

## Critical Issues Found

### 1. BytePort — 18 orphaned stashes, 92 branches, 1 dirty tree
The stashes contain recent WIP (all within 2026-06-24..2026-06-25, many tagged `feat/byte-ui-v2` or `experiment/journey-0217-e`). **These need to be branched before they're accidentally dropped.**

### 2. phenotype-infra — 8 worktrees, 35 branches, leftover audit artifacts
The `wt-pi-d-*` series (8 worktrees) represent active development. The root has numerous leftover artifacts (`_pi_*`, `_audit_*`, `_meta_*`, `_test_*`) that should be gitignored or cleaned.

### 3. PhenoCompose — 79 branches, all old/merged
Most branches are stale `dependabot/`, `renovate/*`, or old `wip/*`. Needs a clean-up pass.

### 4. nanovms — clean but dormant
31 branches, most stale. No active work. Could use hygiene governance.

